---
title: Mexican Pulled Chicken & Bacon Taquitos with Chipotle Sour Cream & Avocado Salsa
description:  How good are taquitos! Just like tacos (but crispier!), these rolled up golden tubes of goodness pack a punch with flavour. These ones have tender pulled chicken in a tomato based sauce, with a chipotle sour cream to heat things up and cool things down. Dig in!
